high_descs: Turn right, move to the other side of the table on the right, turn around to face the spoon on the table.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Bring the spoon to the left sink, on the right.
Wash the spoon in the left sink.
Turn right, bring the spoon to the counter right of the trash can.
Put the cleaned spoon in the drawer right of the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon away in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and go forward toward the stove, then turn right step forward and turn right again to face the white table.
Pick up the spoon on the white table.
Turn right, then turn left and go around the white table to go toward the fridge, then turn right to go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn around, then turn left to go toward the counter next to the trash bin.
Put the spoon in the drawer beneath the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the oven, then turn right and walk up to the wall, turn right again to face the white table.
Pick up the metal spoon off of the white table.
Walk around the white table to the fridge, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the metal spoon in the left sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean spoon.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and begin walking across the room, stop in front of the counter.
Open the leftmost drawer below the counter and put the clean spoon in the drawer, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal spoon in a drawer.
